## What Your Architecture Can and Cannot Handle

### ✅ Features you CAN safely add today

| Feature | Why it works | Effort |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| **New plan tiers** (e.g., Team, Enterprise) | Add one line to `PLANS`, one to `FEATURES`. Hook adapts automatically. | 5 min |
| **New profile fields** (bio, location, pronouns) | Add column to `profiles`, add field to `Profile.jsx` form. Self-contained page. | 30 min |
| **Prompt categories/folders** (client-side filter) | Add a `category` field to prompts, add filter dropdown to existing search UI. | 1-2 hrs |
| **Dark mode** | Your Tailwind config uses CSS variables. Swap variable values in a `.dark` class. Already structured for it. | 1-2 hrs |
| **Prompt export** (download as JSON/CSV) | Pure client-side — read from React Query cache, generate file. No backend needed. | 1 hr |
| **Prompt templates** (pre-filled starters) | Static data, rendered with existing `PromptCard` component. | 1 hr |

### ⚠️ Features you can add AFTER the 5 critical fixes

| Feature | What's blocking | After fixes |
|---------|----------------|-------------|
| **Prompt sharing links** (individual prompt URLs) | No RLS = shared prompts expose other data | Add after RLS |
| **Usage analytics dashboard** | `incrementUsage` race condition + needs pagination | Add after RPC + pagination |
| **User search / discovery** | Profile data is unprotected, plan is self-changeable | Add after RLS + plan protection |
| **Stripe billing integration** | Users can self-upgrade plan, bypassing payment | Add after plan column protection |
| **Prompt versioning** (edit history) | Edit doesn't even save to DB currently | Add after fixing edit flow |

### 🔴 Features that REQUIRE new infrastructure first

| Feature | What's missing | You need to build |
|---------|---------------|------------------|
| **AI auto-tagging** | No backend to run AI calls or store API keys | Supabase Edge Functions |
| **Email notifications** | No server-side execution capability | Edge Functions + email service |
| **Scheduled jobs** (weekly digest, cleanup) | No cron/scheduler | Supabase pg_cron or external scheduler |
| **Webhook integrations** (Zapier, Slack) | No public API endpoint | Edge Functions exposing API routes |
| **Multi-user teams / workspaces** | Data model is single-user only, RLS needs team awareness | Schema redesign + RLS rewrite |
| **Real-time collaboration** | No Supabase Realtime subscriptions configured | New real-time layer |
| **Image/file attachments on prompts** | No upload pipeline exists for prompts | Storage bucket + service function |

